gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

All take the old city as their home, making a living with mutual view;
Later, it becomes a beautiful cloud, and the shade of it is very good.

Here is the translation:

He makes unnecessary haste, then he does not remain; 

He sees servant-making laughter much, if he enjoys play of happy people.

This does what makes happy an infinite play; 
Sukh sagar pranaadhaar;

It has gone to the world with trouble, 
To see the divine form unhappiness.

Here is the translation:

The dead have gone to the sight of God, and it becomes beautiful with company of Munis; 
The days have passed like seeds, the days have passed like a village, and the devotee's name remains.
